headline: Lesaka Technologies (LSAK) Q2 Earnings Meet Estimates
summary: Lesaka Technologies (LSAK) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 0% and 14.70%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
